        <mxCell id="XbR01JuO3Jfv3_1olFRs-1" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="Functional Requirements:" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="170" x="70" y="230" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="XbR01JuO3Jfv3_1olFRs-2" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;div&gt;Design an ecommerce system with following requirements:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;1. User login service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. Search service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. Product catalog service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. Cart service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;5. Order status service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;6. Checkout service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Optimize the product searching and inventory stock management in real time.&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="170" width="320" x="70" y="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="XbR01JuO3Jfv3_1olFRs-3" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="Name: Aditya Singh&lt;div&gt;UID: 23BCS11827&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Section: KRG_2B&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="70" width="120" x="660" y="40" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="XbR01JuO3Jfv3_1olFRs-4" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="1. Users should be able to login&lt;div&gt;2. Users should be able to search products&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. Users should be able to add/remove products from cart&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. Users should be able to make an order and payment&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;5. Users should be able to check their order status&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;6. Users should be able to choose different products from product catalog&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="100" width="400" x="70" y="260" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="XbR01JuO3Jfv3_1olFRs-6" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="Non Functional Requirements:" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="170" x="70" y="370" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="XbR01JuO3Jfv3_1olFRs-7" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="1. System should be able to handle 1.5 million daily active users.&lt;div&gt;2. System should have Availability&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;Consistency&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. Latency: 300-400ms&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. Payment Service must have high consistency&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="100" width="340" x="70" y="400" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
